Gnomes are the backbone of the technological advancement of [[Edion|The Realm of Edion]]. They are the ones who figured out how to merge magic and technology and because of this they are held in high regard, Gnomes are usually found living where there is technology for them to tinker with. Gnomes are one of the longest-lived races, living almost 400 years. 